Package: katana
Version: 1.6.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/projectdiscovery/katana
Description: Fast, passive and active web crawler
 katana is a next-generation crawling and spidering framework designed
 for speed and efficiency. It supports standard and headless crawling,
 form filling, and JavaScript rendering.
